#🍵 Tea Making Site

Welcome to the Tea Making Site! This project is built using HTML & CSS to showcase the process of making a perfect cup of tea.

#🌟 Features

Responsive Design: Works smoothly on all devices.

Beautiful UI: Elegant layout with soft colors and typography.

CSS Animations: Subtle hover and transition effects.

Image Gallery: Showcasing different types of tea.

Easy Navigation: Sticky navbar and smooth scrolling.

📸 Preview



#🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML5

CSS3 (Flexbox & Grid)

#🚀 Installation & Usage

#Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/R0shanShrestha/Bootcamp/edit/main/Day%201/Code

Open the index.html file in your browser.

#📌 Improvements

Here are a few enhancements made:

Improved layout & responsiveness with CSS Flexbox/Grid.

Enhanced typography with Google Fonts.

Added hover effects & animations for a smooth experience.

Implemented sticky navigation for better usability.

#🎯 Future Enhancements

Add a contact form.

Include a dark mode toggle.

#💙 Contributing

Feel free to fork this repository and submit pull requests.

☕ Enjoy your tea-making journey with our site! Happy coding! 🚀


